To "restore" the content of a page using an archive copy, visit the desired copy and click on "Restore" in the top menu.

Copies are archived automatically and on demand. 

To archive a copy of a page, edit the page and use the "Archive" button.

Copy are also archived automatically daily or whenever a new author changes the content of the page.

To read the archived content, simply add "Copy" before the desired page or use the "History" button when editing a page.

